comment: Galloway (NYK) makes contact with Brewer's (HOU) body that affects his layup attempt.
Harden (HOU) makes contact with Porzingis' (NYK) arm that affects his ability to pass.
Thornton (HOU) sets the screen on Afflalo (NYK) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Afflalo (NYK) maintains a legal guarding position on Harden's (HOU) drive.
Porzingis (NYK) maintains legal guarding position as he blocks Harden's (HOU) layup attempt.
Ariza (HOU) and Anthony (NYK) briefly engage and separate as they attempt to establish position in the post.
Jones (HOU) makes contact with the ball after it has touched the backboard and has a chance to score.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of a defensive goaltending violation was upheld.
Afflalo (NYK) and Jones (HOU) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
Jones (HOU) commits a take foul on Anthony (NYK).
Calderon (NYK) establishes legal guarding position prior to the contact from Harden (HOU) away from the ball.
Ariza (HOU) commits a take foul on Anthony (NYK).
Terry (HOU) commits a take foul on Thomas (NYK).
